International Handstand Day: Mathieu Bolillo takes his handstand training to the max

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Acrobatic athlete Mathieu Bolillo shows us his amazing handstand routine down steps as part of the 2016 International Handstand Day celebrations.

